<div class="container" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 30px;">
    âš¡ Performance Tracking Demo
  </h1>

  <div style="background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-radius: 4px;">
    <h2 style="color: #4CAF50; margin-top: 0;">âœ… All Categories Tracked</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
      This page exercises all performance tracking categories. Check the debug bar on the right to see detailed metrics! â†’
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    {{#each categories}}
    <div style="background: var(--color-background-elevated); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
      <div style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 10px;">{{this.icon}}</div>
      <h3 style="color: var(--color-text-primary); margin: 0 0 8px 0;">{{this.name}}</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">{{this.description}}</p>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>

  <div style="background: var(--color-background-elevated); padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
    <h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">ğŸ“Š Test Results</h2>

    <div style="display: grid; gap: 15px;">
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px; background: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1); border-radius: 4px;">
        <span style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Killmails fetched:</span>
        <strong style="color: #2196F3;">{{results.killmails}}</strong>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px; background: rgba(156, 39, 176, 0.1); border-radius: 4px;">
        <span style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Cache hit:</span>
        <strong style="color: #9C27B0;">{{#if results.cached}}âœ… Yes{{else}}âŒ No{{/if}}</strong>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px; background: rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.1); border-radius: 4px;">
        <span style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">System name (from ESI):</span>
        <strong style="color: #f44336;">{{results.system}}</strong>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px; background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1); border-radius: 4px;">
        <span style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Timestamp:</span>
        <strong style="color: #4CAF50;">{{results.timestamp}}</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #FF9800;">
    <h3 style="color: #FF9800; margin-top: 0;">ğŸ’¡ How It Works</h3>
    <ul style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
      <li><strong>Automatic tracking</strong> for infrastructure (DB, Redis, Typesense, HTTP, Templates)</li>
      <li><strong>Manual tracking</strong> for application code using decorators or trackBlock()</li>
      <li><strong>Zero overhead</strong> when tracking is disabled in production</li>
      <li><strong>Categorized breakdown</strong> in the debug bar shows where time is spent</li>
      <li><strong>Detailed timeline</strong> with all operations and their durations</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
    <a href="/" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: var(--color-primary); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600;">
      â† Back to Home
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
